      <title>Advent 就收购 Ryan Reynolds 支持的 Nuvei 进行高级谈判</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-01/advent-in-advanced-talks-to-buy-ryan-reynolds-backed-nuvei</link>
